  <div class="pollmd-help-colors col-12 row rounded">
    <div class="pollmd-help-colors-guide rounded col-12 col-md-12">
      <h4 class="pollmd-help-colors-guide-title col-12"><i>On Images:</i></h4>
      <hr />
      <p>
        You can use the image markdown on our pages by adding the "##image:<i>image_url</i>##" tag to the end of an answer.
        We reccomend not using large images, as it will harm load times.
      </p>
      <p>
        Eg: 
          <h5 style="text-align: left; margin-left: 40px;">Question: What is the best cat pic?</h5>
          <ul style="text-align: left;">
            <li> Cute cat - ##image:https://images-na.ssl-images-amazon.com/images/I/71zkiZbPxdL._SL256_.jpg## </li>
            <li> Funny cat - ##image:https://pbs.twimg.com/profile_images/682493419579699200/xu2JTnH4.jpg## </li>
          </ul>
      </p>
    </div>
